    "body": "Hey @jtremback,\r\n\r\nThis is the correct behavior. There's not blockhash of the current block during the tx execution, as the block is not complete yet. The reason for this is that the block commits to the result of the execution by having merkle Patricia tries of the state and the receipts.\r\n",
